config APP_LINETRACE
	tristate "Drivebase line trace user-space PID app"
	default n
	depends on APP_DRIVEBASE
	depends on LEGO_SENSOR
	---help---
		User-space NSH builtin that follows a line by issuing
		DRIVEBASE_DRIVE_FOREVER continuously while reading reflected-
		light samples from /dev/uorb/sensor_color (mode 1, REFLT,
		INT8 0..100).  Modeled on the pybricks
		`tests/motors/drivebase_line.py` pattern: a tight user-side
		`err = target - reflection(); drive(speed, err * Kp); wait(...)`
		loop.

		Subcommands:
		  linetrace cal              3 s sweep, prints black/white/midpoint
		  linetrace run <speed> <kp> [target] [--max-turn dps] [--hz N]
